<topic id="preferences-tree-editor">
  <title>Tree Editor Preferences</title><prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Configure the Application<indexterm>tree editor</indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Tree Editor</uicontrol> preferences panel is opened from menu <menucascade>
        <uicontrol product="editor developer">Options</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Tree Editor</uicontrol>
      </menucascade> and contains the following preferences:</p>
    <fig id="figure-tree-editor-options">
      <title>The Tree Editor Preferences Panel</title>
      <image href="../img/sa_tree_editor_options.png"/>
    </fig>
    <ul>
      <li><uicontrol>Format and indent on save</uicontrol> - If selected, <ph keyref="product"/>will run the action
          <uicontrol>Format and Indent</uicontrol> (pretty-print) on saving a document edited in the
        tree editor.</li>
    </ul>
  </body>
